          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                " A plastic  scintillator  hodoscope  PiP  was used to",
                " detect protons.  In three separate angular  settings",
                " it  covered polar angles THETA-p = 23 - 152 deg with",
                " a resolution of about 3.5 deg.",
                "Coincident neutrons  were  detected  in  96   plastic",
                " scintillator time-of-flight (TOF) detectors arranges",
                " in 4 layers,  at an average distance of  about  6  m",
                " from  the  target.  The  three TOF positions covered",
                " THETA-n = 19 - 145 deg with resolution  of  about  2",
                " deg,  but  for  present  analysis adjacent detectors",
                " were combined to produce THETA-n  bins  of about",
                " 7.5 deg."
              ]
            }
          ],
